{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"300x–52","heading":"Requirement of reports and audits by States","label":"300x–52 Requirement of reports and audits by States","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300x–52","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch6A/schXVII/ptB/sptiii","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs300x%E2%80%9352","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Amendments2022—Subsec. (a)(3). added par. (3).Pub. L. 117–3281996—Subsec. (a). struck out “and the Comptroller General” after “with the States” in introductory provisions.Pub. L. 104–316"],"amendments":["Amendments2022—Subsec. (a)(3). added par. (3).Pub. L. 117–3281996—Subsec. (a). struck out “and the Comptroller General” after “with the States” in introductory provisions.Pub. L. 104–316"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Report","label":"a Report","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300x–52/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300x–52","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs300x%E2%80%9352%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300x–52/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300x–52/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs300x%E2%80%9352%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the purposes for which the grant received by the State for the preceding fiscal year under the program involved were expended and a description of the activities of the State under the program;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300x–52/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300x–52/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xht